<h1>Memory Game</h1>
<div id="accordion">
  <h3 id="deH3">About</h3>
  <div id="deP">
    Welcome to this Memory Game!<br />
    In this game you can see how alcohol, sports and sleep influences your memory skills.<br />
    There come a few symbols on the screen and they increase with every stage you get.
  </div>
  <h3 id="deH3">How to play</h3>
  <div id="deP">
    When you start the game you see a few symbols. You need to remember these
    in a certain time. After this time the symbols dissapear en you need to
    put him back in the correct order by pushing on the symbols.
  </div>
  <h3 id="deH3">Different stages</h3>
  <div id="deP">
    		There are 3 difficulties between which you can choose.<br />
    Easy: 	&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You have 8 seconds to remember the symbols in the correct order.<br />
    Medium: &nbsp; You have 6 seconds to remember the symbols in the correct order.<br />
    Hard: 	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; You have 4 seconds to remember the symbols in the correct order.
  </div>
  <h3 id="deH3">Extra settings</h3>
  <div id="deP">
    There is an extra option in settings that you can choose to play with 10 instead of 5 different symbols to make it a little bit harder.<br /><br />
    
    You also can choose between 6 different themes of symbols depending on which theme you most like to play with.
  </div>
